# ------Book Entity 測試--------

### 1. 取得所有書籍
### 若沒有書的情況下是空陣列
GET http://localhost:3000/books


### 2. 測試建立新書籍
POST http://localhost:3000/books/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ISBN": "9789571234567",
  "Name": "Node.js 實戰開發",
  "ProductDescription": "深入淺出學習 Node.js 後端開發，從零開始打造企業級應用",
  "Price": 450,
  "InventoryQuantity": 100,
  "Status": 1,
  "Author": "張三",
  "Publisher": "人民郵電出版社",
  "MerchantID": "merchant-uuid-123",
  "images": [
    {
      "imageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/300x400?text=Cover",
      "displayOrder": 0,
      "isCover": true
    },
    {
      "imageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/300x400?text=Back",
      "displayOrder": 1,
      "isCover": false
    }
  ]
}

### 3. 測試建立第二個書籍
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ISBN": "9787115556789",
  "Name": "TypeScript 完全指南",
  "ProductDescription": "TypeScript 從入門到精通，掌握現代前端開發技術",
  "Price": 520,
  "InventoryQuantity": 50,
  "Status": 1,
  "Author": "李四",
  "Publisher": "電子工業出版社",
  "MerchantID": "merchant-uuid-123",
  "images": [
    {
      "imageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/300x400?text=TS+Cover",
      "displayOrder": 0,
      "isCover": true
    }
  ]
}

### 4. 再次取得所有書籍（應該有 2 本書）
GET http://localhost:3000/books


@bookId = 6b0921b8-aa16-4935-9231-302737847dc0
### 5. 根據 ID 取得單一書籍（記得替換成實際的 bookID）
# 從上面的回應中複製 bookID，貼到最上面的 @bookId 變數中
GET http://localhost:3000/books/{{bookId}}

### 6. 根據 ISBN 取得書籍
GET http://localhost:3000/books/isbn/9789571234567

### 7. 更新書籍資訊（記得替換成實際的 bookID）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Price": 399,
  "InventoryQuantity": 80
}

### 8. 更新書籍狀態（下架）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/books/{{bookId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 0
}

### 9. 新增書籍圖片
POST http://localhost:3000/books/{{bookId}}/images
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/300x400?text=New+Image",
  "displayOrder": 2,
  "isCover": false
}

### 10. 刪除書籍圖片（記得替換成實際的 imageId）
@imageId = 10f481f3-d478-4b53-83df-7192224bc65a
DELETE http://localhost:3000/books/images/{imageId}

### 11. 刪除書籍（記得替換成實際的 bookID）
DELETE http://localhost:3000/books/{{bookId}}




